OL,5, A pub where golliwog dolls were seized 
OL,6, by police should not be considered for 
OL,7, "future awards or inclusion in our Good
OL,8, Beer Guide", the Campaign for Real Ale 
OL,9, (Camra) said.                          
OL,11,FCamra said it found it "baffling" that 
OL,12,Fthe White Hart Inn, in Grays, Essex,   
OL,13,Fchose to display the "offensive" dolls.
OL,15,FPolice are investigating after a member
OL,16,Fof the public reported being racially  
OL,17,Fdistressed on 24 February.             
OL,19,FThe pub has been asked to comment on   
OL,20,FCamra's decision.                      
